From Triangle


ğŸ“Œ 613. Shortest Distance in a Line
è§£æ³• 1. absèˆ‡minçš„å…ˆå¾Œé †åº
Select min(abs(p2.x-p1.x)) as shortest
From Point p1, Point p2
Where p1.x != p2.x

ğŸ“Œ 1082. Sales Analysis I
è§£æ³• 1.
With cte As
(Select seller_id, sum(price) As total, rank() Over(Order By sum(price) Desc) AS rnk
From Sales
Group By seller_id)

Select seller_id
From cte
Where rnk=1

è§£æ³• 2. Limit 
Select seller_id
From Sales 
Group By seller_id
Having Sum(price) = (Select Sum(price)
                    From Sales
                    Group By seller_id
                    Order By Sum(price) Desc
                    Limit 1)

ğŸ“Œ 1978. Employees Whose Manager Left the Company
è§£æ³• 1. 
Select employee_id
From Employees
Where salary < 30000
And manager_id Not In (Select Distinct employee_id
                   From Employees)
Order By employee_id

